results.name: A self-generated dragon-like folding sequence.
formula: Limit of m(i+1)=m(i).x(i).Mir(Bar(m(i))), m(1)=0; Mir is the antimorphism Mir(mm')=Mir(m)Mir(m'), Bar the alphabetic morphism Bar(0)=1, Bar(1)=0 and x(i) the letter of rank i into the limit.
results.author: Claude Lenormand (claude.lenormand(AT)free.fr), Feb 14 2001
